Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十八話\N揭開新的血戰序幕\N直逼而來的狼之蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.92,0:02:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊已向京都這邊開始進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.73,0:02:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要開始反攻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也該開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要先佔領京都府都區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二樓的客官們   快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.32,0:02:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新撰組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.39,0:02:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人不眨眼的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府就要被推翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們居然還敢在這裏撒野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說的就這些嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.77,0:02:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論變成什麼朝代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我齊藤還是齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠都不會變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.61,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抗我者必死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是新撰組的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.79,0:03:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那些革命份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.72,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.05,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼可以在這個時候放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.62,0:03:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的理想就快要實現了\N振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡   被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.74,0:03:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們又見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.78,0:04:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的飛天劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是愈來愈厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沖田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先退下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟我還是堂堂的新撰組隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別忘了你有病在身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的眼睛還沒瞎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還看的見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.08,0:05:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓我新撰組第三隊長齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來收拾他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧   緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是牙突劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是很久前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近總是重覆做著同樣的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一二三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.91,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你事情做完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做完的話和我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你在發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再不專心   就不讓你玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心也沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們乖不乖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生產都還順利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.59,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好有小惠的幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.53,0:07:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母子二人都平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是恭喜你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了表示慶祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.04,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我請你們去吃牛肉火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來生了男寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好是男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則長大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是個囉嗦的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在女生面前敢說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.96,0:07:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我們怎麼對付你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認輸了   我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你下次還敢不敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又在發呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去叫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們如果太慢來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肉被吃光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.70,0:08:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.87,0:08:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最近一直夢到從前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.69,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說那個新撰組嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們常和我們作對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.73,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我與他們也交手過好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很厲害的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.04,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是第一第二或第三隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.41,0:09:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都沒有決出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那些幹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.51,0:09:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在幾乎已全都死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於立場不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好以決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.62,0:09:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來為彼此的生命與信念奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.97,0:09:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次聽見你講那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有關過去的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都在等我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.21,0:09:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我自己想的太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.79,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非不祥的預兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.23,0:10:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在還不回來\N不是說只是出去吃個飯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟跑到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃個牛肉火鍋要那麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是多摩來的藥商
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有珍貴的石田散藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫藤田五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.33,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種石田散藥可治跌打損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這裏的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是在這留守的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.54,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此   那就太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.97,0:10:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼睛真小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.08,0:10:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈   是天生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賣藥的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌怎麼這麼粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會也是天生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害的眼力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.73,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就給緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留點小小的警告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是有備而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來真是來者不善
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個傢伙究竟是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.18,0:11:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是衝著劍心來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.42,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓你嘗嘗我的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只不過是小意思而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是打架王左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.47,0:12:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拳頭果真蠻橫有力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼一點都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過在這個時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.71,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拳頭是派不上用場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是日本刀才有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種刀雖然好帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但一下子就被折斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不堪一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小眼睛的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說夠了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.85,0:13:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你的性命著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是乖乖地躺著別動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我已受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你的劍也已經沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就看我的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認輸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等一下還有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不陪大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.03,0:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一副心不在焉的樣子\N也沒吃多少東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是身體不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我又派上用場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛一副大驚小怪的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個人一向都是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來無影去無蹤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我每次辦完事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會想趕快到劍心家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.62,0:14:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見劍心一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是劍心家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰家都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看來很沒精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要我幫你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了   我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的疑慮帶給大家不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.46,0:14:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但即使我把真相告訴他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.40,0:14:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也無法理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有血的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝一杯吧   藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.42,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是叫你齊藤比較順口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛怎麼叫隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.56,0:15:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我不喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.40,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你不會喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我不會喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是喝酒會亂性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.91,0:15:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我一喝酒就會想殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我已經比較能自我控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你請便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就言歸正傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心如今住在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.03,0:16:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一家叫神谷道場的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛我才從那兒來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只可惜他人不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是做事有效率的新撰組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦事這麼有效率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當初你願意加入我們的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還真讓我大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.61,0:16:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦事真是牢靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大吃一驚的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到黑傘事件的幕後指使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是鵜堂刃衛的老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現任元老院議官秘書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.19,0:16:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新志士出身的涉海先生您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.27,0:16:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人本來就可以有多重角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.07,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愛怎樣與我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想好好過完我的下半輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我就心滿意足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人是我最得意的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,替你殺了對家也沒什麼奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.85,0:16:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能除掉我的敵人\N那就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.53,0:17:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟是誰指使你\N去殺緋村劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.73,0:17:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問的也太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們付錢給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要聽命行事就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.57,0:17:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要知道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不必問太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失敬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以後會注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽了會讓你嚇死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作的事就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來我們好好享樂一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不了   我不打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.57,0:17:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣才不會引起別人懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下官就此告別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.08,0:17:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這人就是新撰組第三隊隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治維新後改名藤田五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現為警視廳警捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.75,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人說他比新撰組\N沖田總隊長還要厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.56,0:18:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的武功與緋村劍心不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙一副奸笑的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看了就討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別再發牢騷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.17,0:18:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後和齊藤聯絡\N就是你的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.44,0:18:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.74,0:18:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到我這個維新革命份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.11,0:18:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟會搭上新撰組的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是世事難料啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組的齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.19,0:18:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後就要聽令於我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.46,0:18:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快拿熱水和繃帶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太暗了我看不見傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把燈打亮點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸虧他有堅強的求生意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.76,0:19:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則早就沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他好好睡一覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換我來照顧他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我還要再觀查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去告訴劍心左之助的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛我去道場看了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心似乎有心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別去打擾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.59,0:19:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個藥箱是對方的技倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新撰組的密探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用來偽裝用的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這個刺刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是新撰組慣用的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依這個力道來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.28,0:20:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵定就是齊藤的牙突劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是左手單刃刺法.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.99,0:20:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個新撰組第三隊隊長齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁我不在時找茬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.13,0:20:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟有什麼目的呢
